<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_107" id="53v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_107_r1l14"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu <expan>vveinſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_r1l15">Erb <expan>Camermeıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_107_r1l16">Edler lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . Als vns eẅr edel <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat . vvıe wır den aller </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_r1l17"><expan>durleẅchtıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>fürſt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Sıgmund<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Römıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd ʒu <expan>Vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_r1l18">etc künıg <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> als ſein künıglıch gnade bey vns einge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_r1l19"><expan>rıtte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey . <expan>vnd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> himel eingefürt <expan>ſüll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> himel <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_r1l20">ʒugehörn ſülle etc . das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd wer <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell . das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_r1l21">alſo fürbracht vnd geſagt hett / der hat es niht bas geweſt / vvan wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_r1l22">den <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ den <expan>Römiſch<ex>en</ex></expan> künıg <expan>vnd<ex>er</ex></expan> keinem himel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_r1l23">eingefürt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . Vnd wo wır <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_r1l24"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Cırcu<ex>m</ex>cıſıo<ex>n</ex>ıs</expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nj</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_107" id="53v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad,</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu <expan>Weinsp<ex>er</ex>g,</expan> erb
                                <expan>camermeist<ex>er</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr edel
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, wie wir den aller
                                <expan>durlewchtigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>fürst<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Sigmund<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> und zu
                                <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc. künig,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als sein küniglich gnade bey uns
                                einge<expan>ritte<ex>n</ex></expan> sey,
                            <expan>und<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> himel eingefürt <expan>süll<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> himel
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell zugehörn sülle etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und wer <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        edell das also fürbracht und gesagt hett, der hat es niht bas gewest, wan
                        wir den <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, den <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> künig,
                                <expan>und<ex>er</ex></expan> keinem himel eingefürt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>circu<ex>m</ex>cisio<ex>n</ex>is</expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>ni.</expan>
</ab>
</div>
